00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:49.280
So another way of
rephrasing that, is this

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:51.010
the only triangle
that I could have

00:00:51.010 --> 00:00:53.250
drawn that meets
these conditions?

00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:53.750
Well.

00:00:53.750 --> 00:00:56.291
I can't change this angle if I
want to meet these conditions.

00:00:56.291 --> 00:00:57.850
I can't change
these two lengths.

00:00:57.850 --> 00:00:59.610
And if you keep
this angle constant

00:00:59.610 --> 00:01:00.790
